WEBVTT

00:11.880 --> 00:13.760
Breach the dike

00:14.080 --> 00:16.000
Flood the city

00:35.080 --> 00:36.160
Dongming has fallen

00:36.920 --> 00:38.160
City governor Cao Biaozhi

00:38.320 --> 00:39.320
Before the city fell

00:39.520 --> 00:40.920
Hanged himself

00:41.280 --> 00:42.920
An impregnable fortress

00:43.000 --> 00:44.480
Could only be taken by flooding

00:44.520 --> 00:47.480
Yet tens of thousands of refugees in Jiangzhou

00:47.480 --> 00:48.640
Are also because of me

00:49.120 --> 00:50.480
Heaven's way is balanced

00:50.800 --> 00:52.880
I think my fate

00:53.280 --> 00:54.480
Must have been damaged

00:55.280 --> 00:56.280
Order the entire army

00:56.920 --> 00:58.280
To help rescue nearby refugees

00:58.680 --> 00:59.320
Yes

01:07.120 --> 01:08.800
Oh, quickly relay
